  "detailed_description": "You are the Well of Life...but cannot move!<br><br>An Idle Auto Battler where you face an endless mob of enemies. Simply select a starter weapon and let it play! The life essence of your enemies can be used to upgrade your weapons or unlock new weapons. Defeating bosses gives scrolls you can spend for permanent unlocks or even strengthen your enemies! Survive as long as possible, collect more life essence and challenge the leaderboards!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932740/extras/066d5ed7c1eaf694902a07fc6138e74e.avif?t=1719761551\" width=183 height=156 /></span></td><td>Use life essence collected from your enemies to enhance your weapons!</td></tr></table><br><table><tr><td>    </td><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932740/extras/bc549e46d90f5d12bd27da4368b95959.apng?t=1719761551\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932740/extras/bc549e46d90f5d12bd27da4368b95959.poster.avif?t=1719761551\" class=\"bb_img\" width=79 height=70 /></picture></span></td><td>   </td><td>Press this button, and your weapons will enhance automatically when you collect enough life essence!</td></tr></table><br><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932740/extras/1798d4a6e67c433fd48e07df66e8beba.avif?t=1719761551\" width=157 height=141 /></span></td><td>  </td><td>After each run, spend scrolls obtained from defeating bosses to unlock better weapons, level up your weapons and even strengthen your enemies!</td></tr></table><br><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932740/extras/ca9b4bd7145f3275c0c0b36c2407fa9f.poster.avif?t=1719761551\" width=364 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932740/extras/ca9b4bd7145f3275c0c0b36c2407fa9f.webm?t=1719761551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932740/extras/ca9b4bd7145f3275c0c0b36c2407fa9f.mp4?t=1719761551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></td><td>After a certain number of level ups, weapons will upgrade automatically, gaining new effects!</td></tr></table><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge the leaderboards with your highest score!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932740/extras/a1cfa20c00364ea5005145a204e09b23.avif?t=1719761551\" width=612 height=498 /></span>",
